Author: LinkTheHero1121
Text: I just went through the same thing, sort of. I had to schedule the yearly with the pap and breast exam. Then a regular doctors appointment. I’m 25 and I’ve been needing to do something about my anxiety. I just kind of forced myself to blurt it out, and then the doctor started with questions. Once I just initially said it, it was easier.  On the subject of physicals and paps, I’m not that comfortable with it either. I’m sorry. :(
